  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Curl 7.43.0]]></title>
    <link href="http://plamolinux.github.io/blog/2015/07/23/curl-7-dot-43-dot-0/"/>
    <updated>2015-07-23T17:00:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://plamolinux.github.io/blog/2015/07/23/curl-7-dot-43-dot-0</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>セキュリティホールの修正を含む curl 7.43.0 がリリースされています．詳しくは以下をご覧ください．</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/changes.html#7_43_0">Fixed in 7.43.0 &ndash; June 17 2015</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150422A.html">Re-using authenticated connection when unauthenticated</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150422B.html">Negotiate not treated as connection-oriented</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150422C.html">cookie parser out of boundary memory access</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150422D.html">host name out of boundary memory access</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150429.html">sensitive HTTP server headers also sent to proxies</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150617A.html">lingering HTTP credentials in connection re-use</a></li>
<li><a href="http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20150617B.html">SMB send off unrelated memory contents</a></li>
</ul>


<p>対策パッケージをリリースしました．</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="ftp://plamo.linet.gr.jp/pub/Plamo-5.x/x86/plamo/01_minimum/network.txz/curl-7.43.0-i686-P1.txz">curl-7.43.0-i686-P1.txz (32bit)</a></li>
<li><a href="ftp://plamo.linet.gr.jp/pub/Plamo-5.x/x86_64/plamo/01_minimum/network.txz/curl-7.43.0-x86_64-P1.txz">curl-7.43.0-x86_64-P1.txz (64bit)</a></li>
</ul>

]]></content>
